css-->cascading style sheeets
css gives style to raw html
makes websites responsive i.e suitable for laptop phone etc..
html structure,,,,,css design
css-->modern looking and beautiful

syntax
p       { color:    blue;}
selector  property  value
where     this      set this value

here p means paragraphs
set all paragraphs colour to blue
if only one paragraph should be coloured then id should be given
we can also select using id, class, nested tags
.class
#id

eg2
header , p.intro   {
        |             background_color :red;
        |            border_radius:3px
        |            }
group of selectors   declaration block


3 ways to add css to markup(html)
1.inline css : add css directly to elements using style attribute
     eg: <p style=""></p>
2.internal css : css is kept inside the head tags in <style> tags
        in single file css and markup are kept seperately
3.external css: css is kept seperately in .css style sheet
                and inclue that .css to markup